  "whyus.psychBenefits.b2Title": "Lower Threshold",
  "whyus.psychBenefits.b3Desc": "People check their phone 96 times per day. WhatsApp seamlessly integrates into their natural mobile behavior patterns.",
  "whyus.psychBenefits.b3Mobile": "96x daily phone checks - WhatsApp fits natural mobile habits.",
